The '''BGMI Master Series Season 4''' is an offline tournament organised by [https://nodwingaming.com NODWIN Gaming] in collaboration with [https://www.startv.com/about-us/sports/ Star Sports], with a prize pool of ₹ 1,50,00,000 {{Abbr/INR}} (₹ 1,43,20,000 for Masters Series and ₹ 6,80,000 for Challengers Series)

==About==
===Format===
* '''BGMI Masters Series - Season 4:''''' August 18th - September 14th, 2025
** 28 teams.
** Squads, {{Abbr/TPP}}.

* '''League Stage:''''' August 18th - September 7th, 2025
** 24 invited teams, 21 matchdays.
** 84 matches (4 each day).
*** Each team plays a total of 56 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 4 teams}} qualify for ''Grand Finals.
** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|5th - 12th placed teams}} (8 teams) advance to ''Semi Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|stay|Bottom 12 teams}} advance to ''Playoffs.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Playoffs:''''' September 9th, 2025
** 16 teams, 1 matchday.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|12 teams}} from League Stage.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|4 teams}} from [[BGMI_Challengers_Series|Challengers Series]].
** 4 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} qualify for ''Semi Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 8 teams}} are eliminated.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Semi Finals:''''' September 10th - 11th, 2025
** 16 teams, 2 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from League Stage.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from Playoffs.
** 8 matches (4 each day).
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 12 teams}} qualify for ''Grand Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|down|Bottom 4 teams}} are eliminated.
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''''' September 12th - 14th, 2025
** 16 teams, 3 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|4 teams}} from League Stage.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|12 teams}} from Semi Finals.
** 12 matches (4 each day).

===Points System===
{{Points10|showtb=true}}
====Bonus Points====
* '''Powerplay:''' Double Points for every elimination in the first phase/zone.
* '''Impact player:''''' For League weekends
** Double point for every finish secured by the player chosen by a team's IGL.
* '''Bounty:''''' August 21st - September 7th, 2025
** 10 points for eliminating any Top 4 team according to the League Standings.

